{"tid":2288383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屯公塞車有感","createTime":"2020-11-16T12:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T12:48:52.000Z","uid":133632,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f78e779927c2de2e766964952d55797a62d9cba7","tid":2288383,"uid":133632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"今日收工上巴士 <br />\n就真係踏上這無盡旅途<br />\n<br />\n平時的我都係坐狗鐵返工同收工<br />\n今日諗住坐巴士做返個真黃c<br />\n觀塘上車 塞完龍翔道<br />\n諗住可以好快返屋企食飯<br />\n點知過左長青隧道 又再塞左我半個鐘<br />\n過完大欖諗住 呀！就快可以食得飯<br />\n出完大欖 又塞<br />\n係大概2 3公里的路途<br />\n我見到二架車停係路肩講緊數 肯定係撞完車<br />\n再過多500米左右 又有架車撞q左<br />\n<br />\n作為一個假日司機 <br />\n真係想奉勸一句 唔識渣車就唔好渣<br />\n因為係巴士上有好多同我一樣<br />\n屋企等緊佢地平安返去食飯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當我落車 再望住架巴士<br />\n不敢感歎<br />\n其實我都真係好想做一個真黃c姐"},{"pid":"efe0aa3ed2eb2103f2bafd5744a94c24a4107f60","tid":2288383,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"啱啱搭巴士忍唔住賴左尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"800a35674345f6122a4a17dfcf7e7d8a884e706f","tid":2288383,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe0aa3ed2eb2103f2bafd5744a94c24a4107f60","tid":2288383,"uid":55458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:37:19.000Z","msg":"啱啱搭巴士忍唔住賴左尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:38:17.000Z","msg":"我見到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f9d7a9e333f1eb0d96af705a8924bf4299d6c2","tid":2288383,"uid":79132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:39:00.000Z","msg":"阻人收工要比人燒春袋"},{"pid":"e2eb733b726579ec8fd2eb61d803e06758c3b323","tid":2288383,"uid":165749,"like":0,"